#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:58
msgid "data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A few smouldering wrecks nearby are being observed by a Zoltan vessel, whose"
" captain is speaking on open comms. At first you think he's blindly talking "
"to himself until you realize he's speaking to you. \"Damn Duskbringers, so "
"much pointless bloodshed. This is all the fault of humanity, infecting this "
"galaxy with their diseased ideologies like fascism. If it wasn't for the "
"Rebellion, never would such sinister thoughts have reached our peaceful "
"race.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:60
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "That... doesn't sound right."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:62
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh but it is! It's an ideology born out of the stomach, used by jingoists "
"and fake patriots alike to line pockets with war-time economy and supress "
"free speech. It is a mockery of intellectualism and a cog in the eugenics "
"machine.\" This guy isn't wrong, but the way he speaks makes you realize he "
"may be a bit delusional."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:64
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "If you hate fascists, maybe you can help us with the Rebels?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:66
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan mumbles something to himself. \"Fighting the Rebellion is a "
"futile effort. The disease of fascism has already infected the galaxy, and "
"there's no cure. But you seem young and hopeful. Perhaps a new generation of"
" right-minded individuals can rectify the course of our politics.\" The "
"Zoltan sends some equipment your way. \"I've been holding onto this since "
"the Civil War. I'm not a soldier anymore, I don't need it. Take it, and send"
" the fascists packing!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:71
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_MEDICAL\"]/text"
msgstr "(Medical Crew) Examine his mental state."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:73
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_MEDICAL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew starts asking the Zoltan various questions, trying to probe for "
"tell-tale signs of mental instability. The conclusion seems to be he's "
"experiencing early cognitive decay, a rare malfunction in Zoltan chassis "
"that can cause erratic thought patterns and irregular speech. However, "
"trying to convince him to find a hospital only seems to confuse him more. "
"Strangely, he thinks you're asking him for a reactor tune-up, and agrees."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:78
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave the Zoltan alone."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:84
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_HUMAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Human Crew) Apologise for being solely responsible for inventing fascism."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:86
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FASCISM\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_HUMAN\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan nods. \"Humanity is a species of nothing but pestilent ideas, "
"fermented with political turmoil and selfishness. You have forever ruined "
"this galaxy with partisan concepts like 'democracy' and 'feminism'. It "
"disgusts me. We were once a pure race, until we came into contact with "
"yours. It is known that humans are a warlike race who can only be controlled"
" by manipulating their even greater greed. Take this, and never return.\" "
"It's clear this guy is delusional, but you don't mind free scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:93
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_AUGMENT_MV\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan academy sits docked just outside the beacon perimeter. They're "
"happy to show you the fruits of their labor, and offer something to take "
"home with you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:96
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREE_AUGMENT_MV\"]/choice[1]/text"
