msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:308
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/text"
msgstr "(Boarding Drone) Send a drone to probe the surface."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:310
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Initial scans indicate a network of caves not far underground. You launch a "
"boarding drone and it breaks through the surface into the cavern below."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:315
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:317
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV\"]/choice[@req=\"DRONE_CONTROL_BOARDING\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your drone discovers a vast cave network and evidence of excavation. Buried "
"deep below you find a Zoltan scientist, still hard at work. He tells you "
"that all his colleagues are long dead. You decide not to ask questions and "
"offer to let him join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:326
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"A closer inspection reveals signs of habitation on the surface, but nothing "
"else particularly interesting."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:329
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Sending a shuttle to explore a beckoning cave system you discover signs of a"
" battle - and a still-functioning weapon!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:333
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"A deep scan of the surface reveals a cave system that runs for miles, and "
"what looks like a scrap heap left over from some heavy-duty construction."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:337
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"It looks as if a team could break through the fragile layer of the moon's "
"surface into a hidden cavern."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:339
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to detonate an explosive to break through the surface. [-1}]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:343
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_CHECK\"]/event[4]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Explosives are too valuable to waste on excavation work. Let's get out of "
"here."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:350
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_EXPLOSION\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"A portion of the surface layer is destroyed in an impressive display, "
"revealing miles of caves. You don't have time to fully explore them, but you"
" find some remains of an old subterranean base that could be useful."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:357
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_EXPLOSION\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The explosives are set remotely, but the detonation achieves nothing. What a"
" waste."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:363
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_ODD_MOON_MV_EXPLOSION\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your explosives reveal the 'cave' is actually a secret base, located in a "
"network of bunkers just under the surface. Everyone inside is dead; some "
"Mantis clearly came through here recently. It looks like the Zoltans were "
