"It appears a civilian ship is under attack by a Zoltan ship! You aren't sure"
" why, but it looks like they need help."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:572
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_TOURIST\"]/choice[1]/text"
