"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Free Mantis and Zoltan don't get along well, so it's concerning to see a"
" Free Mantis ship so far into Zoltan space. A ship from the peacekeeper "
"border police has docked with a massive Free Mantis ship, which can't mean "
"anything good."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:658
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Board as well and see what's happening."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:660
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You step into the ship only to find a Peacekeeper violently kicking a "
"defenseless Free Mantis warlord on the ground, who is desperately screaming "
"\"Stop, stop! I not wanting violence, only friendlyness!\", but the Zoltan "
"won't listen."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:662
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pull the Zoltan off of the Free Mantis."

