msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You grab at the Zoltan, pulling them away from the Free Mantis. They shove "
"you away, shouting \"What the hell are you doing? All your precious "
"Federation can do now is interfere with foreign matters, isn't that so? I'll"
" put you in your god damn place!\" The Zoltan gives orders for his men to "
"attack!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:667
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_FREEMANTIS_FRIENDLY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
