#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:782
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_CIVILIANS_HELP\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The civilians manage to fight back the Peace-Keeper forces, who flee from "
"the scene before more casualties can occur. It appears your efforts did not "
"go unnoticed either, and the civilians bring you a large reward for your "
"assistance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:786
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_CIVILIANS_HELP\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The civilians manage to fight back the Peace-Keeper forces, who flee from "
"the scene before more casualties can occur. It appears your efforts did not "
"go unnoticed either, and the civilians bring you a large reward for your "
"assistance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:790
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_CIVILIANS_HELP\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Unfortunately, it seems your efforts were in vain. The civilians are "
"defeated and the Peace-Keepers retake the city. You flee before they can "
"chase you off themselves."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:795
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_PEACE_HELP\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you expected, the Peace-Keepers quickly retake the sector from the "
"Duskbringers and begin making arrests. It appears you chose to help the "
"right side, because the Peace-Keepers have taken note of your efforts at "
"assisting them and pay you in scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:799
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_PEACE_HELP\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears your efforts were in vain, as the Duskbringer forces beat back "
"the Peace-Keepers and slowly take control over the city. As the Capital "
"forces flee, a lone soldier runs to your ship and offers to join you so they"
" can escape."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:803
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_REVOLT_PEACE_HELP\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"While scrapping the hull of the Duskbringer ship, a massive explosion erupts"
" from one of the nearby buildings! Your ship takes some damage but luckily "
"you pull away in time before it can be compromised. Another series of "
"explosions rocks the city, as buildings crumble to the ground! A squadron of"
" Duskbringer bombs descend from the sky, reducing the city to ashes. You fly"
" away as quickly as possible."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:821
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_MANTIS_MV\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your jump interrupts a Zoltan security ship as it follows a Mantis pirate "
"into an asteroid field. They message you, \"Your presence here will continue"
" to be tolerated - but please, do not interfere.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:825
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_MANTIS_MV\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Interfere and save the Mantis ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:827
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_MANTIS_MV\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Sometimes you have to bet on the underdog - even on the rare occasions that "
"the underdog is a Mantis warship. You set off for the heart of the asteroid "
"field and engage the Zoltan there."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:831
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_MANTIS_MV\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
