"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_ZOLTAN_MV\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you hail the refugee ship, a Zoltan ship suddenly jumps into the "
"system... it claims the refugees are criminals, and accuses you of escorting"
" fugitives! Before you can respond, it cuts communications, and powers up "
"its weapons!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:898
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_ZOLTAN_MV\"]/event[2]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:915
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_ARREST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears a pirate ship here is under arrest by a Zoltan ship. They've "
"secretly activated the distress beacon, and have sent you a short message "
"saying \"help\"."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:917
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_ARREST\"]/choice[1]/text"
