#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:951
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_CAPITAL_ARREST_WIN\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears the pirates were slavers. Grateful for your assistance, they "
"offer you one of their 'workers' for free."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:955
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_CAPITAL_ARREST_WIN\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirates appear to be mercenaries, ironically hired to hunt you down by "
"the Rebels. After an awkward silence, you work out a deal, and they promise "
"to lie to the fleet."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:959
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"DISTRESS_CAPITAL_ARREST_WIN\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirates appear to be smugglers. They explain that their client snitched "
"on them and led to their arrest. Now that you've saved them, they offer to "
"sell to you instead."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:966
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan Peace Brigade is under heavy fire at this beacon by a battalion of "
"Rebel fighters. The distress beacon comes from the commanding ship. They "
"appear to be too busy to notice you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:969
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hail them and offer assistance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:971
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It's hard to hear the Zoltan commander over the sounds of gunfire on their "
"ship. \"What?! Oh, you've come to provide assistance? We need all the help "
"we can, there's numerous Rebel ships attacking this system! If you're going "
"to help, be quick about it!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:973
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack one of the smaller Rebel ships."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:975
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Several Rebel ships are scattered around the perimeter, swooping in to "
"assist their comrades when necessary. You pick a ship at random and attack."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:978
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:984
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Take on one of the Elite ships."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:986
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The burden of the attack is being carried out by Elite vessels. You "
"intercept one of them and attack."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:989
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:995
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Take on the ship leading the squadron."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:997
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"A powerful MFK Ace is leading the Rebels. If you can destroy it, the Zoltans"
" might be able to win this battle."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1000
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1008
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_ZOLTAN_RAID\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "This is chaos, leave."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1013
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_BORING_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You salvage the remains of the Rebel ship while the battle rages on in the "
"distance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1016
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_BORING_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1018
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_BORING_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans are too busy dealing with the conflict to reward you, so you "
"decide it's a good time to leave before another Rebel ship attacks you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1023
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_ELITE_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You salvage the remains of the Elite Rebel ship while the battle rages on in"
" the distance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1026
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_ELITE_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1028
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_ELITE_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans are too busy dealing with the conflict to reward you, so you "
"decide it's a good time to leave before another Rebel ship attacks you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1033
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_SELITE_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace has been neutralized. You salvage the remains of the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1036
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_SELITE_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1038
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_SELITE_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Around you the battle begins to die down. The Rebels, watching you defeat "
"their leader, reconsider and begin to jump away. In a matter of minutes the "
"Zoltan forces go from near defeat to conclusive victory."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1040
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_SELITE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Contact the Zoltans."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1042
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"CAPITAL_RAID_SELITE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You have saved us from a terrible defeat. We are grateful for your "
"assistance. Allow me to repay our debt to you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1063
msgid "data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LAWBOOK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A Zoltan peacekeeper is straggling behind its assigned fleet at this beacon,"
" looking for something. They hail you quickly, asking if you can do them a "
"favor."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1066
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LAWBOOK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Inquire further."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:1068
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LAWBOOK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I would not normally ask a stranger of this, but we have found ourselves "
"in a very unfortunate position. We have lost our book of law, a utility "
"required for all Zoltan peacekeepers to have on them at all times. We will "
"not be permitted back into our fleet until we find it... or someone else "
