msgstr "(Shell Crew) Request an exchange with the Zoltan science team."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2096
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ZOLTAN_STUDY\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_SHELL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Overjoyed to come across this opportunity after having remained in Shell "
"space for so long, your Shell has many subjects to discuss, most of which "
"are beyond your understanding. Following a long debate and brainstorming "
"sessions with the Zoltans, they finally are able to return to you, and offer"
" a drone schematic in thanks."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ZOLTAN_STUDY\"]/choice[@req=\"ANCIENT_CONSTRUCTOR\"]/text"
msgstr "(Hibernating Alien) Ask if they know what to do with this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2104
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ZOLTAN_STUDY\"]/choice[@req=\"ANCIENT_CONSTRUCTOR\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Interesting... I have never seen a creature like this. I'm afraid there's "
"not much we can do with it; its current state is unrelated to stasis sleep. "
"However, with a catalyst, such as quantum fuel, you may be able to awaken it"
" again?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2111
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_STUDY_LIST_MV\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew calmly lines up for the Zoltans to take their readings. After a "
"short time, the process is done. They contact you, \"Thank you for your "
"participation in our study. Please accept these small cakes made from stiff "
"dough as well as some scrap.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2115
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_STUDY_LIST_MV\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew calmly lines up for the Zoltans to take their readings. After a "
"short time, the process is done. They contact you, \"Thank you for your "
"participation in our study. Please accept these small cakes made from stiff "
"dough as well as some scrap.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2119
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_STUDY_LIST_MV\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you dock, pirates burst on board and a hostile ship appears on "
"the radar. You hear the Zoltans yell in the distance, \"We're being held "
"hostage!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ministry.xml:2123
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ministry.xml$//eventList[@name=\"ZOLTAN_CREW_STUDY_LIST_MV\"]/event[3]/choice/text"
